{"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Music Metadata Database","anchor":"Music-Metadata-Database","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In the Caches Directory, AutomixIQ keeps a light weight sql database to store the metadata of tracks that have been played for subsequent lookup. This file is called “music.db” and if deleted will be recreated on launch.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Music Analysis Database","anchor":"Music-Analysis-Database","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In the Caches Directory, AutomixIQ keeps a light weight sql database to store the analysis data of tracks that have been played for subsequent lookup. This analysis is required to produce beat-matched transitions. This file is called “paralysis.db” and if deleted will be recreated on launch.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Playback Log","anchor":"Playback-Log","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"AutomixIQ stores offline playback logs for subsequent reporting on a Core Data database, modelled by the following classes:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.cocoapods.SocialRadio\/documentation\/SocialRadio\/AutomixIQPlayLog","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.cocoapods.SocialRadio\/documentation\/SocialRadio\/AutomixIQPlayLogAttributes","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.cocoapods.SocialRadio\/documentation\/SocialRadio\/AutomixIQPlayLogID","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Transition Playback Log","level":2,"anchor":"Transition-Playback-Log","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"AutomixIQ stores offline transition playback logs for subsequent reporting on a Core Data database, modelled by the following classes:",